<div class="content">
<img src="{{plugin_path('PlentyManual')}}/images/omni-channel/online-shop/webshop-einrichten/extras/assets/DE-Mandant-GlobEinstell-ExtDienste-picalike-02-SI.png" alt="DE Mandant GlobEinstell ExtDienste picalike 02 SI">
</div>
<div class="title">Bild 2. <strong>Einstellungen</strong> für picalike</div>
